    <caseIntroduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Coal plays a major role in Chile's energy system, accounting for 18% of the primary energy supply in 2021. The government has made strong decisions to expedite the phase-out of coal from the power sector, with the goal of ceasing operation of all coal-fired plants by 2040 at the latest and retiring 65% of the fleet by 2025.</p>]]></Value>
    </caseIntroduction>
    <caseLockInBlockList>
      <Value><![CDATA[{
  "layout": {
    "Umbraco.BlockList": [
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/b66070faeb1f48b896d205daa0ad0013"
      },
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/dcff319b1d004d15b718d42b174ed930"
      },
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/71da9670c6374b9686421df445098e55"
      }
    ]
  },
  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "5781df7b-a32c-4493-b9fc-90c8e9efebb2",
      "udi": "umb://element/b66070faeb1f48b896d205daa0ad0013",
      "negativePositive": "1",
      "lockInType": [
        "Institutional (and governance)"
      ],
      "bodyText": "<p>The consultation-based approach taken for planning the coal phase-out set a positive precedent, aligning all stakeholders toward the same goal.</p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "5781df7b-a32c-4493-b9fc-90c8e9efebb2",
      "udi": "umb://element/dcff319b1d004d15b718d42b174ed930",
      "negativePositive": "1",
      "lockInType": [
        "Institutional (and governance)"
      ],
      "bodyText": "<p>Consultations with citizens, such as for the preparation of the Long-Term Energy Plan, foster the social support for the phase-out. </p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "5781df7b-a32c-4493-b9fc-90c8e9efebb2",
      "udi": "umb://element/71da9670c6374b9686421df445098e55",
      "negativePositive": "0",
      "lockInType": [
        "Technological (and infrastructural)"
      ],
      "bodyText": "<p>Chile is moving forward with its coal phase-out, but the government has not specified a timeline for phasing out gas. The current framework allows coal units to be converted to gas.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "settingsData": []
}]]></Value>
